| :--------------------------- | :---------------------------------------------- | :------------------------------------------------------------ | :--------------------------------------------------------- | :-------------------------------------------------------------- | :------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Complexity**               | Very Low                                        | Medium (CSS)                                                  | Low (HTML)                                                 | Medium (HTML + CSS)                                             | Very Low                                                |
| **Code Size**                | Minimal                                         | Moderate (CSS for styling)                                    | Minimal                                                    | Moderate (HTML for content, CSS for styling)                    | Minimal                                                 |
| **Browser Support**          | Excellent (all browsers, legacy included)       | Excellent (modern browsers, IE9+ for pseudo-elements)         | Excellent (modern browsers, assistive tech)                | Excellent (modern browsers, assistive tech)                     | Excellent (all browsers, legacy included)               |
| **Custom Styling**           | None (native browser tooltip)                   | Full control (colors, fonts, position, animations)            | None (native browser tooltip, if any)                      | Full control (colors, fonts, position, animations)              | None (native browser tooltip)                           |
| **Rich Content**             | Plain text only                                 | Plain text only (can simulate line breaks with `\A` or `&#xA;`) | Plain text only                                            | Rich HTML content possible (within the described element)       | Plain text only                                         |
| **Accessibility (Visual)**   | Yes (native tooltip)                            | Yes (fully customizable visual tooltip)                       | No (visual only if combined with CSS)                      | Yes (fully customizable visual tooltip)                         | Yes (native tooltip)                                    |
| **Accessibility (Screen Reader)** | Yes (read on hover/focus)                       | No (unless combined with ARIA)                                | Yes (read as element's name)                               | Yes (read as element's description)                             | Yes (read on hover/focus)                               |
| **Touch Device Support**     | Poor (no hover state)                           | Poor (no hover state, unless JS fallback)                     | N/A (primarily for screen readers)                         | Poor (no hover state, unless JS fallback)                       | Poor (no hover state)                                   |
| **SEO Impact**               | Minor (content in `title` is less indexed)      | Minor (content in `data-*` is less indexed)                   | Minor (semantic value for context)                         | Minor (semantic value for context)                              | Minor (semantic value for context)                      |
| **Use Case**                 | Simple, non-critical hints                      | Visually appealing, custom tooltips                           | Providing accessible names for interactive elements        | Providing detailed, accessible descriptions for elements        | Marking abbreviations/acronyms semantically             |
